{"id": 1596, "genre": 1001, "title": "在吃东西这件事上，你总结出了哪些“避雷针”？", "description": "我的钱包和胃容量，不是留给你们这种食物的！（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 5045, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201703291728365DBidbwY8e21zE9c.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-31T03:00:24Z", "options": [{"id": 185856, "content": "不尝尝怎么知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933228}, {"id": 186112, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": "img/option/option/20170401093000IznsEjuoLtHWB4DY.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1}, {"id": 192768, "content": "学校的辣条说，我们是香辣牛肉，鸡肉，螺肉，肉肉肉，其实都是豆制品", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1005686}, {"id": 185857, "content": "各种颜色鲜艳造型好看的小点心", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925523}, {"id": 185858, "content": "么个地方的特色小吃街都一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 588496}, {"id": 186115, "content": "某些。。炸鸡排烤肉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 539921}, {"id": 185860, "content": "每次都信心满满的选了家自己觉得很好吃的店，结果饭桌上却看着同伴抱怨的表情?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988268}, {"id": 185861, "content": "人多的一般质量不咋滴，人多做的就将就了", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976286}, {"id": 186117, "content": "别人介绍的你一定要尝尝才知道是否好吃！\n还有一点，人气旺的小店一般都不会太难吃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928069}, {"id": 185862, "content": "全国各地小吃街都有的小吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 630956}, {"id": 209159, "content": "麥樂酷上的冰淇淋有夠噁的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1045865}, {"id": 185863, "content": "咖啡配沙琪玛有一种别样的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988276}, {"id": 190727, "content": "一到饭点排长队的换了个地然后就，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975122}, {"id": 186120, "content": "优惠套餐其实性价比不高，还不如多攒几天钱，点自己喜欢吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807187}, {"id": 185865, "content": "想尝试一家新的店，去问问在店里吃的客人东西怎么样，而不是看大众点评。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 721625}, {"id": 186121, "content": "尝鲜就得有心理准备", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 942070}, {"id": 185866, "content": "辣鸡食品不碰", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 782841}, {"id": 204299, "content": "强行给自己加戏的；上过舌尖上的中国的；某某电视台推荐；各种祖传、秘制配方；老板脾气大，做生意当成行为艺术的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595170}, {"id": 185867, "content": "去便宜的餐厅不要点原料很贵的东西，比如和牛笑。便宜的东西点的人多流通快，才会比较新鲜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 572, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988286}, {"id": 185869, "content": "越强调安全卫生的食物反而很难吃_(:з」∠)_", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 331311}, {"id": 185870, "content": "辣条在哪里吃都有不一样的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983492}, {"id": 186382, "content": "新来的，冒泡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989607}, {"id": 230671, "content": "点自己认知的吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1110346}, {"id": 185871, "content": "所谓“全麦面包”，配料表上根本没有全麦粉。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 78, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962862}, {"id": 186127, "content": "好看的都不好吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026074}, {"id": 192271, "content": "小时候我妈不让我少吃零食，大了几乎不吃了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958755}, {"id": 185872, "content": "伪吃货飘过", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 874948}, {"id": 185873, "content": "贡茶。。。难喝死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930280}, {"id": 186129, "content": "注意菜单上的小字“图片仅供参考”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988958}, {"id": 188177, "content": "家里做的饭永远是最好的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 993744}, {"id": 185874, "content": "对于“闻起来臭吃起来香”的，对不起，接受不能啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 791745}, {"id": 185875, "content": "大部分中餐厅的的果汁和自带饮料都不要点", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 988310}, {"id": 186131, "content": "照片看着好看的东西一般不怎么样！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989167}, {"id": 190739, "content": "嗯...在有卖西餐的中餐馆绝对不点西餐，某些餐厅二三十块钱一份的牛排不管名字叫什么都不点，卖拉面的地方绝对不点饭", "image": "img/option/option_pic/20170411221450wpxUI8EyoinjCO2fX.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935602}, {"id": 186132, "content": "一个北京人，昨天在同事的撺掇下，排队买了鲍师傅，觉得还是继续吃我的稻香村吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814443}, {"id": 187924, "content": "即使我喜欢吃香菜，在约饭的时候也千万不能点香菜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965631}, {"id": 216341, "content": "不要看到顾客排很长队就跟风啊，很可能前面排队的人都不知道在卖什么东西，因为反正大家都在排队嘛，肯定还不错喽。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064591}, {"id": 206871, "content": "一般各种社交软件推的真的没有那么好吃，而且人还TMD多，排那么久买的东西真的没有软件上面说的好吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039157}, {"id": 185879, "content": "KKK旅途兔兔咯啦咯", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900740}, {"id": 185880, "content": "某地小吃，一般都不地道。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 979697}, {"id": 186904, "content": "作为总能踩雷的倒霉蛋来说，点招牌或经典是最好的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978603}, {"id": 194328, "content": "最近在公众号上做过营销的，如果去实体店门可罗雀，肯定东西不灵的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1009185}, {"id": 287770, "content": "装修好的，大部分吃的环境", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377399}, {"id": 185882, "content": "要紧的是把好：病从口入这一关（至少有不少病是跟吃有关吧？）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645296}, {"id": 186138, "content": "用普通材料做出来但是价格却特别贵的东西普遍不好吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989191}, {"id": 186650, "content": "明星开的店纯属圈钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 559606}, {"id": 185883, "content": "打高光的宣传照，实物大多暗淡也不对自己胃口", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915794}, {"id": 187931, "content": "男朋友推荐你喝的炒鸡好喝的奶茶", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 874658}, {"id": 190491, "content": "门口摊子，毕竟我有别人都吃不到头发，就我吃的到头发体质，最多的时候一天吃到两回头发?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984831}, {"id": 185884, "content": "985211学校食堂饭菜味道都不会太差，穷游的时候可以进去垫个午饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 186, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147386}]}